prompt: Ugh, your website's recommendations are useless – last time you sent me to some shady rental place that didn't even have cars! I need to rent a car in Dallas, Texas, but I'm not trusting your single suggestion again. I want to see EVERY car rental company in Dallas, right now, so I can actually compare them myself. And if I see a decent one, I want to book it immediately for June 15th, 2025 at 10 AM. Don't you dare mess this up again.
